  <para>
    In the toolbox container, you
  can install any tool you want with <command>zypper</command> and then use the
  tool without rebooting your system.
  </para>
  <para>
    To leave the container, just type <command>exit</command>. Remember that the container
    stays in the same state as you exit it. If you want a clean environment, you need to
    remove the <literal>toolbox</literal> container first. For the removal procedure, see <xref linkend="toolbox-starting-container"/>.
  </para>
  
